{"tid":686954,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"屌臭World of tank","createTime":"2018-06-01T18:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T12:34:11.000Z","uid":184570,"like":9,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"dd2813d68595742dd20bc136ee60d00b35af9c59","tid":686954,"uid":184570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:30:12.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n德國線架Tiger(P)難撚升都閪咁 玩7咩 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n架車廢撚到仆街 一炮得個240 你老母都要成100K經驗先解到下架車 仲要長時間排T9場<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔撚明 點解明知架車咁撚垃圾 點解唔可以做d公平機制 係撚都要人地上去睇人面色<br />\n<br />\n做一隻game做到你咁撚多BUG真係屌你老母失9敗 <br />\n<br />\n明明遊戲係比人放鬆既 屌你我就越玩越撚嬲 越撚大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係好想棄game 但係我都課唔少金落去 又唔撚捨得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴打我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n E只game d設計師極有可能個腦真係有問題 <br />\n<br />\n屌你如果唔係因為坦克game得佢一隻 我真係臭系都唔撚玩E只on9 game"},{"pid":"d948e0f331a9ef536ba208789a638de9156d6ebb","tid":686954,"uid":40903,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T19:01:53.000Z","msg":"走啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 成個連登已棄"},{"pid":"abe9b9cd84965af701cda38c519cdd6d14f29f64","tid":686954,"uid":996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T19:03:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾game嚟，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c881d60c208ab3adcbd83e6dd9d50e8a32cc3f25","tid":686954,"uid":39838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T19:06:20.000Z","msg":"呢隻game係game 玩人<br />\n喺佢所謂隨機分配入場同埋有無敵RNG加乘底下<br />\n同一架車可以上一場底階照開無雙下一場頂階比人一炮秒"},{"pid":"67b8f5eb142993b595cdb7506e7053db9711c0cc","tid":686954,"uid":156795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T19:06:36.000Z","msg":"